source.name: U.S. Air Force Smart Operations for the 21st Century News
source.description: An RSS feed documenting news related to Air Force Smart Operations for the 21st Century (AFSO 21), the Air Force's version of Lean Six Sigma. Lean Six Sigma is a civilian business strategy which is designed around the idea of making a product or procedure "smarter, faster and cheaper."
